{"tid":51414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子探監變坐監 關32小時賠465萬","createTime":"2016-12-23T07:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T14:48:04.000Z","uid":36906,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a58ce9376de3d408c86644b9df60390cc4a53695","tid":51414,"uid":36906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"美國芝加哥一名男子去監獄探監，被錯誤鎖在一個囚室內32小時，最後獲獄方賠償約465萬港元，平均1小時獲賠14萬5千港元，創下當地最短時間冤獄的最高賠償紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這名「探監變坐監」的男子名叫法拉（Farad Polk），他因為兒子犯毒被判坐監，早前到獄中探望兒子，但法拉在到獄室時，不知為何竟迷路，錯誤地去到一間空置的囚室，並被反鎖在裡面。<br />\n<br />\n法拉在囚室裡曾喊救命，但無任何人發現，他在斷水斷糧的情況下，被困囚室32小時，最後他撬開天花灑水系統，觸動消防系統，驚動消防員到場，獄方這時才派員到囚室營救他。<br />\n<br />\n法拉其後控告監獄，並獲賠償60萬美元(約465萬港元)和解，據美國傳媒報導，這賠償金額，創下當地最短時間冤獄的最高賠償紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/1652926-%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B4%E5%86%A4%E7%8D%84%EF%BC%9F%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%8E%A2%E7%9B%A3%E8%AE%8A%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%A3-%E9%97%9C32%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%B3%A0465%E8%90%AC?r=w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9-plastic-post%2F1652926-%25E6%259C%2580%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E5%2586%25A4%25E7%258D%2584%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%258E%25A2%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%259D%2590%25E7%259B%25A3-%25E9%2597%259C32%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%25B3%25A0465%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fr%3Dw&d=K2ZWUtMstStDIes0vZ4PKgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f02f6ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/1652926-%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B4%E5%86%A4%E7%8D%84%EF%BC%9F%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%8E%A2%E7%9B%A3%E8%AE%8A%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%A3-%E9%97%9C32%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%B3%A0465%E8%90%AC?r=w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人想坐?<br />\n坐:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔住:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913dcc8716225892c3b14219e09c5ccc2fbef867","tid":51414,"uid":6809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-